Text:
GIANNIS511, let me be the 1st to say thank you for posting this!

i am amazed by the demand for this one. TPB at this moment tracks over 1,000 seeders and another 150 leechers for this issue.

On a related note, i uploaded the Complete TV series of Spectacular Spider-Man:
http://thepiratebay.sx/torrent/8081651/The_Spectacular_Spider-Man_Complete_TV_Series

Could use some seeding help ;)

Thanks for your UL for your other post as well.

Not reading this drivel until they bring Parker back.  What a stupid way to end the other series.

@STFmaryville: Thanks for your support and your kind words!I believe the reason for having so many seeders in Superior Spider-Man is that people stopped buying it due to the death of Peter Parker.
@GMTN: I totally agree that they should not have let Peter die and reactions like yours (not reading the comic) are justified. Although when (and I believe it will be very soon judging on today's ending ) Marvel understand their mistake, you will probably have to read the whole series from the beginning to know what is going on.
I am sure PP is not dead. It is a comic. I read my first spider-man back in 1976. PP is not dead. From a danish fanboy. Super THANX to the uploaders!
whew! just read it. did you guys read the letters page? wow... lots of negativity.

Here's the Variant Cover - Someone could add to next torrent the variants, just go to Marvel.com, no need to scan - http://marvel.com/images/gallery/issue/46471/images_from_superior_spider-man_2013_2_mcguinness_variant/image/944403/full
Dan Slott is a fat stupid bastard who cant write a goddamn comic. He needs to just jackoff and leave the writing to others!
